title: Tour de France 2013 Highlights Stage Three
description:
When i get a few seeds to take over then your on your own.


ITV4 HD
Mon Jul 1



Presenter - Gary Imlach, Commentator - Phil Liggett, Commentator - Paul Sherwen, Guest - Chris Boardman, Reporter - Ned Boulting


Action from stage three of the prestigious race, a 145.5km journey from Ajaccio to Calvi on the island of Corsica. The concluding day of the 'Grand Depart' on the French island featured another medium-mountain course that was unlikely to favour the sprinters, but could indicate which of the expected contenders for the general classification is in good early form. Presented by Gary Imlach, with commentary by Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen, analysis by Chris Boardman and reports by Ned Boulting.
